170	⏳Comment récupérer les photos originales ? 	comment-recuperer-les-photos-originales-287	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	287	2025-01-02 11:24:20	2026-05-27 18:57:40.352	\N	\N	\N	<p>Je souhaites r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer les photos de mon &eacute;v&eacute;nement, sans le cadre.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Probl&egrave;me &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>		f		<h2>Les &eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735817485429" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735817485429" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 - Sortir du logiciel Selfizee</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735817485429" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Pour quitter le logiciel Selfizee, veuillez faire le raccourci : ALT + F4</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/18f6c0e3-f08b-4434-ba97-aa09626a006f.png" alt="" width="460" height="187" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735817506908" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735817506908" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 - Allez dans les dossiers de la borne</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735817506908" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Pour acc&eacute;der aux dossiers, veuillez faire le raccourci : Windows + E</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/fee49be6-6b03-4cea-81fe-2c5962467694.png" alt="" width="460" height="188" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735817529695" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735817529695" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 - Allez dans les dossiers de l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735817529695" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans le chemin d'acc&egrave;s, tapez "%programdata%" et allez dans le dossier "Konitys" puis "Selfizee" et "Events"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/99c9bedf-df94-4ddc-bcaa-62fbde3d54de.png" alt="" width="526" height="152" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez ensuite sur le code logiciel correspondant &agrave; l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735817551128" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735817551128" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 4 - R&eacute;cup&eacute;rez les photos originales</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735817551128" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur le dossier "M&eacute;dia", "Photo", "Original"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Vous pouvez ensuite r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer les photos originales</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<p><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Un souci ?&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez toutes les &eacute;tapes&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment faire pour r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer les photos originales d'un &eacute;v&eacute;nement ?</li>\r\n<li>Comment enlever le cadre de mes photos prisent lors de mon &eacute;v&eacute;nement ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
171	⏳Comment mettre un nouveau cadre sur des photos vierges ?	comment-mettre-un-nouveau-cadre-sur-des-photos-vierges-288	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	288	2025-01-02 14:14:15	2026-05-27 18:57:40.379	\N	\N	\N	<p>Toutes les photos ont &eacute;t&eacute; imprim&eacute;es avec un cadre qui n&rsquo;&eacute;tait pas bon. Il faut donc remettre le bon cadre sur toutes les photos.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Application &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/uploads/posts/e73bd9c3-09c5-43a4-840f-a4ad950aed97.png" alt="" width="158" height="155" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/uploads/posts/eb570f11-1796-4e98-9b4c-612096ebb898.png" alt="" width="159" height="158" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Vid&eacute;o explicative :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/a2a8e00a-3270-4a54-81ea-3b80f0d84a9f.mp4#t=0.4" alt="" width="594" height="319" /></p>		f		<h2>&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735824336909" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735824336909" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 - R&eacute;cup&eacute;rez les photos vierges dans la borne photo et r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer le bon cadre</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735824336909" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Pour r&eacute;ussir cette &eacute;tape, veuillez trouver le lien et suivre les &eacute;tapes indiqu&eacute;es :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="caret-color: #54667a; color: #000000; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ecf0f1;">[lien num_article=287 titre=⏳Comment r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer les photos originales ? ]</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735824474454" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735824474454" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 - Pr&eacute;parez les fichiers</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735824474454" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Cr&eacute;ez un dossier avec :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- le bon cadre en PNG</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- un sous-dossier avec toutes les photos vierges</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- cr&eacute;er un sous-dossier "CADRE VF"</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735824572767" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735824572767" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 - Cr&eacute;ez une action sur Photoshop</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735824572767" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Ouvrir Photoshop et faire glisser une premi&egrave;re photo vierge</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans l'onglet "Fen&ecirc;tre", cliquez sur "Action"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Si c'est la premi&egrave;re fois, cr&eacute;er un ensemble</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/6055dce1-b92c-4139-bacd-092c8a300603.png" alt="" width="662" height="377" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Ensuite, cr&eacute;ez une action</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/6f675010-d395-4681-8684-85e82d028d67.png" alt="" width="663" height="377" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Une fois l'action enregistr&eacute;e, celle-ci va se lancer</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/aa6599e3-2aeb-463f-a056-39369c7b5d2b.png" alt="" width="409" height="228" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Redimensionnez l'image et le plan de travail (au final, le plan de travail doit faire 1844x1240 px)</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Faire glisser le cadre que vous souhaitez utiliser</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- D&eacute;verouillez la photo</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/8bafc24e-a67d-4d14-b822-5bab1972826b.png" alt="" width="409" height="432" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- S&eacute;lectionnez les deux cadres, puis clic droit pour fusionner les calques</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- De nouveau clic droit pour "Aplatir l'image"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Maintenant allez dans la fen&ecirc;tre "Fichier" et "Enregistrer sous"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">ATTENTION : enregistrez en JPEG dans le sous dossier que vous avez cr&eacute;&eacute; "CADRE VF"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Enfin, dans le menu des actions, arr&ecirc;tez l'enregistrement</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/2f279ea3-0bdb-4f44-91c1-eecca09e8005.png" alt="" width="407" height="228" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1735826369663" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1735826369663" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 4 - Automatisez l'action pour l'ensemble des photos</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1735826369663" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Allez dans l'onglet "Fichier" puis "Automatisation" et "Traitement par lots"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/16759735-cc2d-4e15-b737-876a9b494f06.png" alt="" width="419" height="330" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans la partie "Source", s&eacute;lectionnez le dossier contenant les photos vierges</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/0fed51e4-4ee1-4aee-b755-e6e832bb457f.png" alt="" width="535" height="253" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans la "Destination", s&eacute;lectionnez le dossier o&ugrave; seront les photos avec cadre</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/456c83d7-c3ae-46ed-9bae-3f8cdf502324.png" alt="" width="540" height="253" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Enfin, cliquez sur "OK" pour lancer l'automatisation</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">NB : Il est &eacute;galement possible de retravailler la photo avec un cadre Polaro&iuml;d. Il faut simplement inverser la taille du plan de travail et bien positionner le Polaro&iuml;d avant de d&eacute;verouiller la photo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Suivre attentivement chaque &eacute;tape</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment faire pour changer le contour sur toutes mes photos ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer mes photos vierges ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
172	⏳Comment mettre à jour mon événement ?	comment-mettre-a-jour-mon-evenement-289	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	289	2025-01-06 12:02:06	2026-05-27 18:57:40.418	\N	\N	\N	<p style="margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none; font-size: 12pt;">J&rsquo;ai r&eacute;alis&eacute; des modification sur mon studio et je veux mettre &agrave; jour sur la borne.</span></p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/17e12512-ee16-464e-89cc-aa11a3f60420.png" alt="" width="378" height="345" /></p>		f		<h2>&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736163884012" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736163884012" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 - Connectez la borne &agrave; internet</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736163884012" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Si votre borne n'est pas connect&eacute;e &agrave; internet, veuillez suivre les &eacute;tapes de la fiche suivante :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><a href="https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/164/sscategorie/4">https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/164/sscategorie/4</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736163923650" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736163923650" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2 - Acc&eacute;dez &agrave; l'espace "Configuration de l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement"</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736163923650" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Une fois le logiciel Selfizee lanc&eacute;, cliquez sur le point d'interrogation en bas &agrave; droite de votre &eacute;cran</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/5ee28257-c949-4ac3-aeb9-a6b740ff2aa3.png" alt="" width="625" height="350" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- entrez le code de votre &eacute;v&eacute;nement ou le code administrateur</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/454cfa68-130b-4682-ad93-20f135e0282d.png" alt="" width="624" height="371" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736163940709" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736163940709" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 3 - Mettre &agrave; jour</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736163940709" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur le bouton "Mise &agrave; jour"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/7cb44d0b-b825-40aa-ba1e-3d7a33779e29.png" alt="" width="622" height="295" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- retournez sur la fl&eacute;che en haut &agrave; gauche pour retourner &agrave; l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/9701af07-a8c5-4732-bda9-59d1d791229f.png" alt="" width="623" height="264" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<h2><strong>Un souci ?&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>V&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>		<ul>\r\n<li>J'ai modifier mon cadre sur le manager mais il ne change pas sur la borne, que faire ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment faire pour modifier mon cadre sur la borne ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment faire une mise &agrave; jour de mon &eacute;v&eacute;nement sur la borne ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
173	⏳Comment régler le décompte photo ?	comment-regler-le-decompte-photo-290	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	290	2025-01-06 13:16:28	2026-05-27 18:57:40.445	\N	\N	\N	<p style="margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none; font-size: 12pt;">Je souhaite r&eacute;duire/augmenter le temps avant la prise de photo.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none; font-size: 12pt;">Le temps est trop long/trop court entre deux photos.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-kerning: none;">&nbsp;</span></p>		<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 36px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; color: #2c2b2e; font-size: 22px !important;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/17e12512-ee16-464e-89cc-aa11a3f60420.png" alt="" width="328" height="300" /></p>		f		<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 36px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; color: #2c2b2e; font-size: 22px !important;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736168656663" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736168656663" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 - Acc&eacute;dez &agrave; l'espace "Configuration de l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement"</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736168656663" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Une fois le logiciel Selfizee lanc&eacute;, cliquez sur le point d'interrogation en bas &agrave; droite</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/f392d8b3-1395-4dc4-8f2a-e94fda18fd70.png" alt="" width="498" height="279" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Entrez le code de votre &eacute;v&eacute;nement</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736168676180" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736168676180" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2 - Allez dans les configurations</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736168676180" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur le bouton "Configuration"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/832385ea-0c1e-4062-9cd9-342d6d420a92.png" alt="" width="503" height="253" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736168696141" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736168696141" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 3 - R&eacute;glez le d&eacute;compte photo</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736168696141" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans l'onglet "Prise de vue", vous pouvez donc r&eacute;gler le d&eacute;compte avant la prise de la premi&egrave;re photo</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/de8a6c8b-5385-4bba-93cc-f6cffba910f5.png" alt="" width="505" height="321" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736168731550" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736168731550" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 4 - R&eacute;glez le d&eacute;compte entre 2 photos sur un multi-shoot/ bandelette</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736168731550" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans le m&ecirc;me onglet, vous pouvez r&eacute;gler le d&eacute;compte des photos suivantes&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/1f4b0732-de74-45b3-a671-5bf17568f049.png" alt="" width="501" height="304" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736168752356" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736168752356" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 5 - Retournez &agrave; l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736168752356" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur la fl&eacute;che en haut &agrave; gauche pour retourner &agrave; l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/cb89f0cd-09fe-49b7-aa84-8d79d56ad51e.png" alt="" width="496" height="259" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes.</li>\r\n<li>Suivez les &eacute;tapes dans l'ordre.</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment modifier le d&eacute;compte photo ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment r&eacute;duire le d&eacute;compte photo ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment augmenter le d&eacute;compte photo ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
