onfigurations</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736250161716" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur le bouton "Configuration"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/7fe97b7e-7562-4d80-bcc7-b8b3bfaf69f3.png" alt="" width="716" height="360" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736250192825" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736250192825" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 - Activez/d&eacute;sactivez les filtres</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736250192825" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans l'onglet "Filtres", vous pouvez donc activer ou d&eacute;sactiver les diff&eacute;rents filtres</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/37d9cc44-ac7f-42ec-ac48-5bb96006ba25.png" alt="" width="714" height="406" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736250214284" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736250214284" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 4 - Retournez &agrave; l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736250214284" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur la fl&egrave;che en haut &agrave; gauche pour retourner &agrave; l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/c154d6bc-c240-4685-8a36-877738911ed9.png" alt="" width="712" height="376" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment activer les filtres sur le Photobooth ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment d&eacute;sactiver les filtres sur le Photobooth ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
183	✅ Les paramètres ont sauté	les-parametres-ont-saute-300	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	300	2025-01-07 14:42:56	2026-05-27 18:57:40.763	2025-01-07 14:42:56	\N	\N	<p>La borne affiche "OUT OF SERVICE" ou "BORNE HORS SERVICE" ?</p>		<h1><strong>Probl&egrave;me &agrave; consulter :&nbsp;</strong></h1>\r\n<p><strong><img src="/uploads/posts/b6f20890-6ae5-4234-89f6-17b9c27aa6fb.png" alt="" width="378" height="267" /></strong></p>		f		<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 36px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; color: #2c2b2e; font-size: 22px !important;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736260314182" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736260314182" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 - Connectez la borne &agrave; internet</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736260314182" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si votre borne n'est pas connect&eacute;e &agrave; internet, veuillez consulter la fiche suivante :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="caret-color: #54667a; color: #000000; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ecf0f1;">[lien num_article=164 titre=✅ Connexion &agrave; Internet ou partage de connexion]</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736260329709" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736260329709" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 - Allez dans l'espace administrateur</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736260329709" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Restez appuyer quelques secondes en haut &agrave; gauche de l'&eacute;cran pour entrer dans l'espace administrateur.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Le mot de passe est sur la photo ci-dessous.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/0d0396a0-ebb4-4b31-8fe7-134a9e55e92d.png" alt="" width="389" height="219" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736260350577" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736260350577" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 - Allez dans les r&eacute;glages de la borne</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736260350577" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur le logo "r&eacute;glages" en bas &agrave; droite.</div>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/ec1f1f9c-c80d-40a1-9c76-76a06662bf78.png" alt="" width="391" height="220" /></p>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "DEVICES" ou "P&Eacute;RIPH&Eacute;RIQUES" au milieu, en bas.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Remettre chacun des r&eacute;glages en cliquant sur les boutons &nbsp;"..."&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/c4f93f04-b7e7-42be-adf4-d320bd83a4c9.png" alt="" width="386" height="223" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cam&eacute;ra : cliquez sur "Microsoft Cam&eacute;ra Front"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Printer : cliquez sur "DP-QW410"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Microphone : "Microphone (Realtek High Definition Audio (SST))</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- GPU : "Intel<span style="-webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px;">&reg;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;HD Gaphics 615"&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736260387633" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736260387633" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 4 - Remettre la borne dans la langue de votre choix</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736260387633" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans l'onglet APPLICATION en bas &agrave; droite, cliquez sur language et mettre la langue de votre choix.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/a1e74bb2-3639-46f3-b550-c6f612c25255.png" alt="" width="386" height="221" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736260402321" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736260402321" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 5 - Remettre l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736260402321" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur la fl&egrave;che en haut &agrave; gauche pour retourner en arri&egrave;re.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/69ce37d3-cad1-429a-b4e7-74e52628f17f.png" alt="" width="388" height="263" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Allez dans "Mes &eacute;v&eacute;nements" pour r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement ou "T&eacute;l&eacute;charger un &eacute;v&eacute;nement" pour en configurer un nouveau.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/56c156aa-86b7-4e30-b361-b88884b6e078.png" alt="" width="386" height="99" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes</li>\r\n<li>Recommencez la manipulation</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment faire quand il y a borne hors service ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment remettre les param&egrave;tres ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Les param&egrave;tres ont saut&eacute;s, que faire ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi ma borne est en anglais ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>R&eacute;glages</li>\r\n<li>Hors service</li>\r\n</ul>
184	⏳ Le logiciel crache 	le-logiciel-crache-301	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	301	2025-01-07 14:53:02	2026-05-27 18:57:40.795	\N	\N	\N	<p>Que faire lorsque le logiciel crache ?</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/17e12512-ee16-464e-89cc-aa11a3f60420.png" alt="" width="378" height="345" /></p>		f		<h2>R&eacute;solution du probl&egrave;me :</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Il suffit de relancer le logiciel Selfizee qui se situe sur le bureau Windows.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736261431129" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736261431129" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Cliquez sur le logiciel Selfizee</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736261431129" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Placez-vous devant l'&eacute;cran de la borne photo.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/ca3420f9-f4b0-4c1f-b75b-6f7299882857.png" alt="" width="475" height="475" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Double cliquez sur le logiciel Selfizee pour le relancer</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/0dcff3b8-bdb0-459b-ae37-2a20e91b988f.png" alt="" width="518" height="518" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<p><strong>Le probl&egrave;me sur le logiciel persiste ?</strong></p>\r\n<p>&Eacute;teignez puis rallumez l'&eacute;cran du photobooth en consultant les fiches suivante :</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/249/sscategorie/6">https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/249/sscategorie/6</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/248/sscategorie/6">https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/248/sscategorie/6</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>		<ul>\r\n<li><span id="p89">Le photobooth ne fonctionne plus</span></li>\r\n<li><span id="p96">Le photobooth ne r&eacute;agit pas</span></li>\r\n<li><span id="p97">Le photobooth est bloqu&eacute;</span></li>\r\n<li>Le logiciel ne fonctionne pas</li>\r\n<li>Je ne peux plus utiliser le photobooth</li>\r\n<li>Le logiciel crache</li>\r\n</ul>
185	⌛Le téléchargement de l'événement ne fonctionne pas	le-telechargement-de-l-evenement-ne-fonctionne-pas-302	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	302	2025-01-07 16:22:04	2026-05-27 18:57:40.831	\N	\N	\N	<p>Impossible de t&eacute;l&eacute;charger mon &eacute;v&eacute;n&eacute;ment.</p>\r\n<p>Ce message s'affiche lorsque vous souhaitez t&eacute;l&eacute;charger votre &eacute;v&egrave;nement</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-kerning: none;">&nbsp;</span></p>		<h1><strong>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</strong></h1>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/17e12512-ee16-464e-89cc-aa11a3f60420.png" alt="" width="378" height="345" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>		f		<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 400; line-height: 36px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; color: #2c2b2e; font-size: 22px !important;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736264431565" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736264431565" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 - V&eacute;rifiez votre connexion internet</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736264431565" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Si la borne n'est pas connect&eacute;e &agrave; internet, veuillez suivre les &eacute;tapes de la fiche suivante :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><a href="https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/164/sscategorie/4">https://help.selfizee.fr/fr/assistance/detail/164/sscategorie/4</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736264450179" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736264450179" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 - Mettez la borne &agrave; l'heure</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736264450179" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si la borne n'est pas &agrave; l'heure, le t&eacute;l&eacute;chargement du code &eacute;v&eacute;nement peut &ecirc;tre impossible.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Retournez sur le bureau avec les touches ALT+F4 du clavier</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/2f5a1741-9a8c-4c22-956f-6a6485a83635.png" alt="" width="428" height="174" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans la barre des t&acirc;ches, recherchez "Modifier la date et l'heure"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/c992ea7b-4f44-4e1e-b9e5-c099e547a37b.png" alt="" width="580" height="387" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS'; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none; font-size: 12pt;">- D&eacute;sactivez et r&eacute;activez l&rsquo;option &ldquo;D&eacute;finir l&rsquo;heure automatiquement&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS'; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS'; -webkit-text-stroke-width: initial; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;"><span style="font-kerning: none; font-size: 12pt;"><img src="/uploads/posts/ac0fed45-31db-4d17-a251-4f19f30910c4.png" alt="" width="583" height="379" /></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Retournez sur le logiciel et t&eacute;l&eacute;charger votre &eacute;v&eacute;nement</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Si &ccedil;a ne fonctionne toujours pas :&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736266087285" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736266087285" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 - T&eacute;l&eacute;chargez l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement manuellement</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736266087285" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Sur le manager, "T&eacute;l&eacute;charger le fichier d'installation manuel" et enregistrer le fichier zip sur une cl&eacute; USB pour le mettre directement sur la borne</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/7a2caca3-95a1-4f10-ae26-c3efbe4877a3.png" alt="" width="581" height="258" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Ins&eacute;rez la cl&eacute; USB dans la t&ecirc;te de borne et coller le fichier zip dans les document de la borne</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/a71e1e15-71ba-46a0-91b9-d593f25bd636.png" alt="" width="582" height="351" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Relancez le logiciel Selfizee et appuez en haut &agrave; gauche de l'&eacute;cran pour entrer dans l'espace administrateur et taper le code</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/a570145f-ac38-4a94-ac3e-2e00db3aa0de.png" alt="" width="588" height="396" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "T&eacute;l&eacute;charger un &eacute;v&eacute;nement"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/807086c1-d8bc-415e-a118-9187e6933b4d.png" alt="" width="587" height="84" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "Import manuel" en bas de l'&eacute;cran&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/dfa5d130-bb05-4f74-ae5e-6975062d1f0a.png" alt="" width="588" height="393" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Ouvrir le fichier&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/ad2303e2-40c9-4343-9158-61afadb3a89f.png" alt="" width="594" height="389" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Le t&eacute;l&eacute;chargement se lance !&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Je n'arrives pas &agrave; t&eacute;l&eacute;charger mon &eacute;v&eacute;nement ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi ma borne n'est pas &agrave; l'heure ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment forcer le t&eacute;l&eacute;chargement de mon &eacute;v&eacute;nement ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
187	✅ Les photos sont trop claires/lumineuses 	les-photos-sont-trop-claires-lumineuses-304	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	304	2025-01-08 10:23:34	2026-05-27 18:57:40.91	2025-01-08 10:23:34	\N	\N	<p>Lorsque vous vous prenez en photo, vous trouvez que celle-ci est trop claire/lumineuse.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/17e12512-ee16-464e-89cc-aa11a3f60420.png" alt="" width="328" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/70034f5c-8e7c-4b2c-a53b-37ab9d5e320d.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></p>		f		<h2>&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736327996052" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736327996052" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 - Ouvrez l'espace administrateur</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736327996052" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">-&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">Une fois devant la borne, touchez l'&eacute;cran en haut &agrave; gauche.</span></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">- </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">Entrez le mot de passe donn&eacute; par l'assistance.</span></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/99af3b4e-f4aa-4a30-8b35-3cfdd5bb8b1c.png" alt="" width="581" height="328" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736328228561" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736328228561" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 - Acc&eacute;dez aux r&eacute;glages de l'appareil photo</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736328228561" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">- Cliquez sur le bouton des r&eacute;glages en bas &agrave; droite de l'&eacute;cran.</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/bec29a53-5514-4880-9484-21c8ad2ffb1e.png" alt="" width="597" height="305" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">- Rendez-vous dans l'onglet des p&eacute;riph&eacute;riques situ&eacute; au milieu en bas et cliquez sur le bouton "R&eacute;glages" &agrave; c&ocirc;t&eacute; du p&eacute;riph&eacute;rique "Canon EOS XXXXX" (XXXXX &eacute;tant le mod&egrave;le de votre appareil).&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/uploads/posts/ef85ed26-fec7-4c89-8ffe-c480c60dd1c6.png" alt="" width="601" height="307" /></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736328773626" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736328773626" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 - R&eacute;glez la quantit&eacute; de lumi&egrave;re per&ccedil;ue par l'appareil photo</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736328773626" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">-&nbsp;&nbsp;Depuis les r&eacute;glages de l'appareil photo, cliquez sur l'onglet "ISO" et activez le r&eacute;glage "ISO auto".</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/d5ac5f75-ee53-4a9e-943b-8c92e2622a2c.png" alt="" width="123" height="394" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">- Cliquez sur la fl&egrave;che en haut &agrave; droite pour revenir en arri&egrave;re.</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/3fb45135-19d8-4f84-a889-9fcc62bb8e7a.png" alt="" width="595" height="336" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736329649148" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736329649148" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 4 - V&eacute;rifiez les r&eacute;glages de l'image</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736329649148" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;">- Rendez-vous dans l'onglet "Image" en bas &agrave; gauche de l'&eacute;cran et cliquez sur "r&eacute;glage de l'image".</span></span></span><span id="docs-internal-guid-17cf0d77-7fff-29f2-eb09-a0edee4d4ec5" style="color: #000000;"></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/uploads/posts/70aca670-c89d-4d8c-93c3-d0fd9e307f81.png" alt="" width="591" height="329" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;">- R&eacute;alisez l'action "double cliquez pour d&eacute;marrer". </span></span></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/uploads/posts/9b0c510a-fe2a-45bd-bd76-f53dc7ccd9b7.png" alt="" width="593" height="334" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">- V&eacute;rifiez que les r&eacute;glages "couleurs" soient tous positionn&eacute;s sur "0". Si ce n'est pas le cas il suffit de cliquer sur le 0 de chaque ligne.</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/uploads/posts/84f310df-21b9-4df6-ae66-ca5a39822264.png" alt="" width="196" height="295" /></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Si les photos sont toujours trop claires/lumineuses :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736331381238" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736331381238" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 5 - V&eacute;rifiez manuellement que le flash de l&rsquo;appareil photo ne soit pas activ&eacute;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736331381238" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">- Rendez-vous &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur de la t&ecirc;te en retirant la porte arri&egrave;re pour pouvoir atteindre l'appareil photo.</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000;">- Cliquez sur le bouton menu de l'appareil photo puis allez sur la ligne "Contr&ocirc;le du flash".</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/uploads/posts/178b5edb-8bb5-46c8-9ad7-837f6e086452.png" alt="" width="405" height="302" /></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">- Cliquez sur "&Eacute;mission &eacute;clair" puis "D&eacute;sactiv&eacute;e".</span></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img src="/uploads/posts/60168013-9d0b-4cb8-8ef6-aab890cbce9c.png" alt="" width="403" height="297" /></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Faire attention &agrave; la luminosit&eacute; de l'endroit o&ugrave; se situe le photobooth</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Mes photos sont trop claires&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Je souhaites assombrir mes photos</li>\r\n</ul>
188	Accédez à l'espace administration	accedez-a-l-espace-administration-305	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	305	2025-01-09 14:58:59	2026-05-27 18:57:40.939	\N	\N	\N					f		<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736247754296" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 996.296875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736247754296" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 - Acc&eacute;dez &agrave; l'espace "Configuration de l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement"</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736247754296" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Une fois le logiciel Selfizee lanc&eacute;,&nbsp;<span style="caret-color: #54667a; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">cliquez sur le point d'interrogation en bas &agrave; droite de l'&eacute;cran</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="caret-color: #54667a; color: #000000; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><img src="/uploads/posts/6c74070b-0a42-4af4-9a18-1ad8a1f65623.png" alt="" width="648" height="363" /></span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="caret-color: #54667a; color: #000000; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">- Entrez le code de votre &eacute;v&eacute;nement</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736247775498" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 996.296875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1736247775498" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 - Allez dans les configurations</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1736247775498" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="font-size: 16px; caret-color: #54667a; color: #000000; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;">- Cliquez sur le bouton "Configuration"</span></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><span style="font-size: 16px; caret-color: #54667a; color: #000000; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;"><img src="/uploads/posts/ba371f55-b983-492c-858d-cb22551e8497.png" alt="" width="647" height="325" /></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1736247801157" class="panel-heading" role="tab">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>	\N				
189	⏳un doute sur les différents formats ? 	un-doute-sur-les-differents-formats-306	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	306	2025-01-16 13:53:46	2026-05-27 18:57:41.006	\N	\N	\N	<p>Vous souhaitez conna&icirc;tre le format pour la cr&eacute;ation d'un cadre, d'un &eacute;cran, d'un fond vert ou encore d'un photocall ?&nbsp;</p>		<p><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><strong>APPLICATIONS &Agrave; UTILISER :&nbsp;</strong></span></p>		f		<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737035229388" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737035229388" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">FORMATS CADRES</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737035229388" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>Paysage :&nbsp;</strong>15 x 10 cm</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>Portrait :</strong>&nbsp;10 x 15 cm&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>Bandelette :</strong>&nbsp;5,5 x 15 cm&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737035242907" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737035242907" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">FORMAT FOND VERT</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737035242907" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si vous souhaitez cr&eacute;er votre fond vert, il est important de respecter les dimensions suivantes :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">1844 x 1240 pixels&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737035256565" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737035256565" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">FORMAT PHOTOCALL</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737035256565" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si vous souhaitez cr&eacute;er votre photocall, il est important de respecter les dimensions suivantes :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">12992 x 12992 pixels</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737035497590" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737035497590" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">FORMATS &Eacute;CRAN D'ACCUEIL</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737035497590" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>- Classik :&nbsp;</strong>1920 x 1080 pixels&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>- Spherik :&nbsp;</strong>1200 x 800 pixels&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>	\N				
190	✅ Démonter et remonter la tête de borne 	demonter-et-remonter-la-tete-de-borne-307	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	307	2025-01-20 11:18:42	2026-05-27 18:57:41.031	2025-01-20 11:18:42	\N	\N	<p>J'ai besoins d'avoir acc&egrave;s &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur de la t&ecirc;te de la borne.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/7db2b058-73f5-49a0-870b-c8751a933b03.png" alt="" width="300" height="383" /></p>		f		<h2>APER&Ccedil;U VID&Eacute;O :&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="300" height="150">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/29a776cb-6bad-4ba4-b904-be1a984201e4.mov#t=0.4" />\r\n</video></p>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes</li>\r\n<li>Suivre la vid&eacute;o</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>L'assistance me demande d'ouvrir la t&ecirc;te de borne, comment faire ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Quels vis enlever pour ouvrir la t&ecirc;te du photobooth ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
191	✅Purger l'imprimante	purger-l-imprimante-308	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	308	2025-01-20 13:21:32	2026-05-27 18:57:41.072	2025-01-20 13:21:32	\N	\N	<p>Lorsque vous avez install&eacute; la borne Classik et allum&eacute; l'imprimante, plusieurs photos s'impriment sans s'arr&ecirc;ter.</p>		<h2>Probl&egrave;me &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/924db811-127c-4eaa-b25b-3799a1da765f.png" alt="" width="309" height="81" /></p>		f		<h2>&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737379144465" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737379144465" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 : Touchez l'&eacute;cran &agrave; gauche&nbsp;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737379144465" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<p>- Lorsque vous &ecirc;tes devant l'&eacute;cran de la borne Spherik, cliquez en haut &agrave; gauche de l'&eacute;cran.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;">- Veuillez rentrer le mot de passe administrateur donn&eacute; par l'assistance.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><img src="/uploads/posts/7d1fc0bb-400e-48bc-ba3b-bba15698aa44.png" alt="" width="500" height="277" /></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737379149372" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737379149372" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 : Allez dans les r&eacute;glages</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737379149372" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;">- Cliquez sur les trois petits traits en bas &agrave; droite de l'&eacute;cran pour acc&eacute;der aux r&eacute;glages.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/be59928e-cdfe-4ce8-b8a8-b3f9a69b0fa4.png" alt="" width="492" height="286" /></p>\r\n<p>- Allez dans les "P&eacute;riph&eacute;riques".</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/aec087ce-1116-47a1-82f5-d6a51c4e336f.png" alt="" width="492" height="302" /></p>\r\n<p>- Cliquez "r&eacute;glages" de l'imprimante.</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><img src="/uploads/posts/807e7ebd-d2d7-483a-9b4c-3c29586a4158.png" alt="" width="484" height="302" /></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737379159564" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737379159564" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 : Purgez l'imprimante</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737379159564" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Cliquez sur "PURGER" afin de remettre le nombre d'impression en attente &agrave; 0.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/uploads/posts/e98127f4-cc36-44c7-9abc-a030d29843c8.png" alt="" width="483" height="291" /></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Les photos s'impriment sans s'arr&ecirc;ter&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Pourquoi des photos s'impriment ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
204	✅Vider les événements passés	vider-les-evenements-passes-321	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	321	2026-02-02 14:11:13	2026-05-27 18:57:43.781	2026-02-02 14:11:13	\N	\N	<p>Vous n'arrivez plus &agrave; imprimer car votre espace de stockage est satur&eacute; ?&nbsp;</p>		<p>A savoir : il est important de supprimer des &eacute;v&eacute;nements lorsqu'il est pass&eacute; d'environ 3-4 mois pour &ecirc;tre sur de ne pas avoir besoin des photos.&nbsp;</p>		f		<pre>Allez sur l'&eacute;cran de la Borne.<br />Appuyez 2 secondes l'angle en haut &agrave; gauche de l'&eacute;cran.<br /><br /><img src="/uploads/posts/f7d79866-1695-410a-b0c1-434f52fb9bce.png" alt="" width="525" height="328" /><br /><br />Vous allez arriver sur l'espace administrateur.<br />Appuyez sur la touche "&amp;123"<br /><br /><img src="/uploads/posts/3799000a-58d3-4044-aff3-be599252f3d2.png" alt="" width="524" height="295" /><br /><br />Saisissez le mot de passe !"&lt;&gt;':;/? &agrave; l'aide du clavier tactile.<br /><br /><img src="/uploads/posts/900091f1-c878-401a-a600-6d26a9f92759.png" alt="" width="522" height="294" /></pre>\r\n<pre>Cliquez sur "mes &eacute;v&eacute;nements" <br /><br /><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/424e14b9-2cae-4ceb-a2f2-fcb0bfa27fdf.png" alt="" width="525" height="354" /></pre>\r\n<pre>Appuyez sur les trois traits et cliquez sur "Archiver" <br /><br /><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/18d1eb09-29c4-4bd7-b1d0-8d9452ad69d5.png" alt="" width="527" height="356" /><br /> <br />Cliquez sur "Supprimer" <br /><br /><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/2ca38452-a1b5-4309-8c11-76054202d49f.png" alt="" width="526" height="357" /></pre>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Mon imprimante ne fonctionne plus.</li>\r\n<li>Je n'arrive plus a prendre de photo.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Mes photos ne s'enregistres pas.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment supprimer des &eacute;v&eacute;nements de ma borne ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment gagner en stockage ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Je n'ai plus de stockage sur ma borne photo ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi le photobooth n'imprime plus ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
193	⏳ La tablette s'allume mais pas la lumière ? 	la-tablette-s-allume-mais-pas-la-lumiere-310	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	310	2025-01-21 10:45:09	2026-05-27 18:57:41.165	\N	\N	\N	<p>Vous avez fini d'installer la borne photo, mais la lumi&egrave;re ne s'allume pas.&nbsp;</p>				f		<h2>&Eacute;TAPE ILLUSTR&Eacute;ES :&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737456304409" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737456304409" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 1 : Raccordez la t&ecirc;te du photobooth</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737456304409" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737456340529" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737456340529" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 2 : Raccordez l'alimentation du photobooth</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737456340529" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1737456358986" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1737456358986" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;TAPE 3 : Reliez l'alimentation &agrave; une prise secteur</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1737456358986" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>	\N				
195	✅Changer la palette de couleur pour les imprimantes DS620	changer-la-palette-de-couleur-pour-les-imprimantes-ds620-312	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	312	2025-08-07 08:16:58	2026-05-27 18:57:41.219	2025-08-07 08:16:58	\N	\N	<p>La couleur a l'impression de vos photos ne sont pas comme &agrave; l'&eacute;cran ?&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>Connectez-vous &agrave; la borne photo.</p>		f		<h2>R&eacute;solution du probl&egrave;me :</h2>\r\n<div class="attention" style="font-size: medium; font-weight: 400;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Attention :</strong></span>&nbsp;Veuillez vous assurer que la borne soit b&ccedil;en connect&eacute;e &agrave; internet et que l'imprimante est bien allum&eacute;e avant d'effectuer l'op&eacute;ration.</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754553818355" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754553818355" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 : S&eacute;lectionnez la bonne imprimante</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754553818355" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Dans la barre de recherche Windows, tapez "Gestion des couleurs"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Vous allez arriver dans les p&eacute;riph&eacute;riques, s&eacute;lectionnez l'imprimante concern&eacute;e.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/b6f256f5-d8fd-4d0d-8d1a-4f6e2fca44d8.png" alt="" width="532" height="396" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Profils ICC : DS620_141105-7.icc.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">S'ils ne sont pas pr&eacute;sent : Envoyer le dossier DS620-R0.icc sur la borne dans le dossier "mes documents"&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754554446778" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754554446778" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2 : Ajouter le fichier DS620-R0</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754554446778" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Cliquez sur "Ajouter"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/92114ba1-6f25-4a96-b504-764700107d5b.png" alt="" width="523" height="270" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si vous vous rendez compte que le profil n'est pas pr&eacute;sent, cliquez sur "parcourir" et s&eacute;lectionnez le fichier ICC que vous avez t&eacute;l&eacute;charg&eacute; dans "Mes Documents"&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Validez en cliquant sur "OK" puis sur "d&eacute;finir le profil par d&eacute;faut"&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Les couleurs ne sont pas bonnes &agrave; l'impression&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Les couleurs changent&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Pourquoi les couleurs &agrave; l'impression ressortent mal ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi je n'ai pas les m&ecirc;mes couleurs &agrave; l'&eacute;cran et &agrave; l'impression ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
196	✅Bourrage papier ++ / papier coincé dans l'imprimante DNP DS620	bourrage-papier-papier-coince-dans-l-imprimante-dnp-ds620-313	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	313	2025-08-07 09:27:39	2026-05-27 18:57:41.25	2025-08-07 09:27:39	\N	\N	<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: auto; color: #212529; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: sans-serif;"><span style="white-space: normal;">L'imprimante est en erreur et vous rencontrez des probl&egrave;mes de papier coinc&eacute;.&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: sans-serif;"><span style="white-space: normal;">Voici les &eacute;tapes &agrave; r&eacute;aliser afin de r&eacute;soudre le probl&egrave;me.<br /><br /><br /></span></span></pre>		<h2>Inventaire mat&eacute;riel :</h2>\r\n<p>Rapprochez-vous de l'imprimante Classik DNP DS620 &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur du photobooth.</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/0f4fc305-74f4-4af8-93ea-1bf533013845.png" alt="" width="338" height="396" /></p>		f		<h2>Aper&ccedil;u du probl&egrave;me :</h2>\r\n<p>Mes photos ne s'impriment plus et le voyant&nbsp;<strong>POWER vert</strong>&nbsp;<strong>RIBBON orange</strong>&nbsp;et&nbsp;<strong>ERROR rouge</strong>&nbsp;de l'imprimante sont allum&eacute;s. Cela signifie qu'il y a soit un probl&egrave;me avec le papier, soit avec le ruban d'encre.</p>\r\n<p>Vous ouvrez l'imprimante et vous vous apercevez que le papier est froiss&eacute;, il s'agit d'un&nbsp;<strong>bourrage papier</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/2e9b0f17-704e-4bd6-854a-1ca051f3255f.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/29d57b6b-1c7b-431f-b6ce-5d272326917a.png" alt="" width="462" height="335" /></p>\r\n<h2>R&eacute;solution du probl&egrave;me :</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="attention" style="font-size: medium; font-weight: 400;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Attention :</strong></span>&nbsp;Veuillez &eacute;teindre l'imprimante, attendez 5 secondes et rallumez-la.</div>\r\n<p>L'imprimante va se r&eacute;initialiser et le papier sera lib&eacute;r&eacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cela &eacute;vite de d&eacute;chirer le ruban d'encre dans la plupart des cas.</strong></p>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754555219546" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754555219546" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 : Ouvrez l'imprimante</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754555219546" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Utilisez le levier d'ouverture (en bleu) pour tirer sur le m&eacute;canisme et ouvrir l'imprimante.</div>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/9b6697aa-5806-44c7-bfd7-82f99dc9a6a9.png" alt="" width="462" height="296" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754555271701" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754555271701" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2 : Ouvrez le capot de l'imprimante</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754555271701" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Tirez sur le levier de l'imprimante puis le levez le capot pour acc&eacute;der &agrave; la bobine papier.</div>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/ad225639-220a-42d1-9eec-86b7b9a9100f.png" alt="" width="466" height="338" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754555329690" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754555329690" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 3 : Enlevez le papier coinc&eacute;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754555329690" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Vous constatez que le papier est coinc&eacute; dans l'imprimante. Tirez sur le papier pour enlevez la bobine.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/5a201eb7-6c94-40ca-9698-4abc22e5cc53.png" alt="" width="464" height="297" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754555460062" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754555460062" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 4 : Coupez le papier </a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754555460062" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Coupez la partie probl&eacute;matique avec des ciseaux ou un cutter afin que le d&eacute;but de la bobine papier soit parfaitement droit.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/231f7346-d2dd-4b2e-9c2e-b71840fbbcfa.png" alt="" width="448" height="395" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754555607722" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754555607722" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 5 : V&eacute;rifiez le cheminement du papier</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754555607722" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Une d&eacute;coupe peut &ecirc;tre rest&eacute;e dans l'acheminement que prend le papier.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Prenez une photo vierge qui est sortie lors du calibrage et faite passer celle-ci dans le chemin du papier mais aussi dans l'unit&eacute; de d"coupe &agrave; l'avant de l'imprimante.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/fee00173-bd11-46cb-b6b8-7681f881ebaa.png" alt="" width="220" height="292" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/uploads/posts/ef99e529-caca-48dd-bc2a-7325c0f76f38.png" alt="" width="217" height="293" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754558286634" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754558286634" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 6 : V&eacute;rifiez les cales de jeu du capot</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754558286634" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si les photos test sortent bien mais qu'il y a un bourrage &agrave; l'impression, v&eacute;rifiez la pr&eacute;sence des cales de jeu du capot d'imprimante.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/959dbc66-0936-4b34-b5f4-16b993c1875e.png" alt="" width="442" height="228" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Si toutefois l'une d'entre elles est manquante il y a moyen de se d&eacute;panner en collant un morceau de carton dur.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Vous avez besoin d'aide ou avez un doute pour remettre le papier ? Consultez la fiche [lien num_article=66 titre=✅ Changement consommable imprimante Classik] afin de remettre correctement le consommable dans l'imprimante.</p>\r\n<h2>Aper&ccedil;u vid&eacute;o :</h2>\r\n<p>Vid&eacute;o illustrant le d&eacute;coupage du papier d&eacute;fectueux et la remise en marche de la bobine papier :</p>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="294" height="147">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/9463ca08-92a4-497f-b67c-e08145040426.mp4#t=0.4" /></video></p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Bourrage papier</li>\r\n<li>Le papier ressemble est pli&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le papier est coinc&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le rouleau est d&eacute;chir&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le papier est d&eacute;chir&eacute;</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Bourrage papier</li>\r\n<li>Le papier ressemble est pli&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le papier est coinc&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le rouleau est d&eacute;chir&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le papier est d&eacute;chir&eacute;</li>\r\n</ul>
197	✅Modifier l'ouverture de la focale de l'appareil photo	modifier-l-ouverture-de-la-focale-de-l-appareil-photo-314	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	314	2025-08-07 09:38:51	2026-05-27 18:57:41.275	2025-08-07 09:38:51	\N	\N	<p>Aussi appel&eacute;e "zoomer d&eacute;zoomer"&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/70034f5c-8e7c-4b2c-a53b-37ab9d5e320d.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></p>		f		<h2>&Eacute;tapes illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754559098208" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754559098208" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 </a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754559098208" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Demandez &agrave; une personne de se placer &agrave; l'endroit de prise de vue souhait&eacute;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754559132153" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754559132153" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754559132153" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Placez vous derri&egrave;re la borne photo et ouvez la porte arri&egrave;re.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754559157039" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754559157039" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 3</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754559157039" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Appuyez sur le bouton d&eacute;crit sur la photo ci-dessous :</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/bcbf2ef1-fd70-4959-9c4a-932b58bc8a73.png" alt="" width="187" height="202" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754559327848" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754559327848" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 4</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754559327848" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Vous obtiendrez une vue en temps r&eacute;el sur l'&eacute;cran.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/7ea378c2-2bc9-472c-a888-fba02f9e9e9b.png" alt="" width="188" height="195" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754559380960" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754559380960" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 5</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754559380960" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Effectuez le r&eacute;glage en pivotant la bague d'ouverture.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/e8e85b13-2750-4a82-b66f-74617b2df317.png" alt="" width="193" height="184" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>ATTENTION DE BIEN PRENDRE EN COMPTE LE CONTOUR DE L'ANIMATION QUI LUI N'APPARAIT PAS SUR L'&Eacute;CRAN DE L'APPAREIL</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez chacune des &eacute;tapes&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Faire attention &agrave; la luminosit&eacute; de l'endroit o&ugrave; se situe le photobooth</li>\r\n<li>Je ne vois pas assez le fond derri&egrave;re moi lors de la prise de photo</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment modifier l'ouverture ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment changer la prise de vue ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
199	✅ Paramétrer un appareil photo M200	parametrer-un-appareil-photo-m200-316	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	316	2025-08-07 13:05:01	2026-05-27 18:57:42.161	2025-08-07 13:05:01	\N	\N	<p>Mon appareil photo Canon M200 est mal configur&eacute;.</p>				f		<h2>&Eacute;tapes Illustr&eacute;es :</h2>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">ATTENTION</span>&nbsp;<span style="color: #e0182d; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: #fddcd0;">L'appareil photo doit &ecirc;tre&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #e0182d; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: #fddcd0;">branch&eacute; au photobooth</strong><span style="color: #e0182d; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: #fddcd0;">&nbsp;et &ecirc;tre&nbsp;</span><strong style="color: #e0182d; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: #fddcd0;">allum&eacute;</strong><span style="color: #e0182d; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: #fddcd0;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #e0182d; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; background-color: #fddcd0;">lors de l'op&eacute;ration.</span></p>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754570737197" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754570737197" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 : Position du s&eacute;lecteur rotatif</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754570737197" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/9846f967-d2b2-4ddd-921b-9dced12ca838.png" alt="" width="326" height="306" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Positionnez le s&eacute;lecteur rotatif sur le logo appareil photo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754570822152" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754570822152" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2 : Mettre l'appareil en fran&ccedil;ais</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754570822152" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Appuyez sur la touche Menu puis d&eacute;placez-vous vers l'onglet "Cl&eacute; &agrave; molette".</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Validez en appuyant sur le centre du pac&eacute; directionnel.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Allez sur le menu 2 et allez sur Langage pour s&eacute;lectionner Fran&ccedil;ais.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Sur le m&ecirc;me menu, montez sur Mode Veille et s&eacute;lectionnez D&eacute;sactiv&eacute;.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Faire de m&ecirc;me pour le Mode &Eacute;co.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/a0e5fe72-be63-473b-848d-66ff5210cc25.png" alt="" width="292" height="297" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754571380675" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754571380675" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 3 : Configurez les derniers r&eacute;glages</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754571380675" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Appuyez sur la touche Menu et d&eacute;placez-vous sur le menu appareil photo.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/f05b6830-4e4d-4cc8-9b5f-9d9b2ac8336f.png" alt="" width="285" height="224" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Faites OK</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">S&eacute;lectionnez le mode de prise de vue "AV"</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/abc9686d-30c0-4403-abd6-5b8fd73639cf.png" alt="" width="283" height="305" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1754571554317" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1754571554317" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 4 : D&eacute;sactivez le Wifi et Bluetooth</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1754571554317" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Allez dans le menu communication.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/ab190f5e-9d4b-43cb-afd5-1a12b09a18f6.png" alt="" width="524" height="333" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Appareil photo non configur&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Mauvais r&eacute;glages sur le Canon M200</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment configurer mon appareil photo ?</li>\r\n</ul>
200	✅ Brancher la borne photo	brancher-la-borne-photo-317	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	317	2025-09-22 14:09:39	2026-05-27 18:57:42.548	2025-09-22 14:09:39	\N	\N			<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>Avant toute chose, v&eacute;rifiez que votre photobooth Spherik est bien mont&eacute;. Tr&eacute;pied d&eacute;ploy&eacute;, t&ecirc;te du photobooth correctement install&eacute;e et imprimante bien fix&eacute;e.</p>		f		<h2>Aper&ccedil;u vid&eacute;o :</h2>\r\n<p>Vid&eacute;o illustrant le raccordement &agrave; r&eacute;aliser pour le bon fonctionnement et la bonne alimentation de la borne photo Spherik.</p>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="300" height="150">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/1aae6ecb-9feb-4484-82f1-71c86e0c17e7.mov#t=0.4" />\r\n</video>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<h2>Un souci ?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Rev&eacute;rifiez tous les branchements</li>\r\n<li>Les raccordements sont-ils bien enfonc&eacute;s dans les diff&eacute;rent(e)s ports et prises?</li>\r\n<li>La prise secteur est-elle bien fonctionnelle ?</li>\r\n</ul>		
201	✅ Papier coincé dans l'imprimante DNP DS620	papier-coince-dans-l-imprimante-dnp-ds620-318	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	318	2026-01-12 11:05:02	2026-05-27 18:57:42.918	2026-01-12 11:05:02	\N	\N	<pre style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: auto; color: #212529; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-family: sans-serif;"><span style="white-space: normal;">L'imprimante est en erreur et vous rencontrez des probl&egrave;mes de papier coinc&eacute;.&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: sans-serif;"><span style="white-space: normal;">Voici comment r&eacute;soudre le souci.</span></span></pre>		<h2>Inventaire mat&eacute;riel :</h2>\r\n<p>Rapprochez-vous de l'imprimante Classik DNP DS620 &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur du photobooth.</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/0f4fc305-74f4-4af8-93ea-1bf533013845.png" alt="" width="338" height="396" /></p>		f		<h2>Aper&ccedil;u du probl&egrave;me :</h2>\r\n<p>Mes photos ne s'impriment plus et le voyant&nbsp;<strong>POWER vert</strong>&nbsp;<strong>RIBBON orange</strong>&nbsp;et&nbsp;<strong>ERROR rouge</strong>&nbsp;de l'imprimante sont allum&eacute;s. Cela signifie qu'il y a soit un probl&egrave;me avec le papier, soit avec le ruban d'encre.</p>\r\n<p>Vous ouvrez l'imprimante et vous vous apercevez que le papier est coinc&eacute;, il s'agit d'un <strong>bourrage papier </strong>et il est possible qu'un bout de papier soit coinc&eacute; &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/2e9b0f17-704e-4bd6-854a-1ca051f3255f.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" /></p>\r\n<h2>R&eacute;solution du probl&egrave;me en vid&eacute;o :</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="398" height="199">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/cefac7dd-26a5-4906-8631-bbf371f88718.mp4#t=0.4" /></video></p>	\N				<ul>\r\n<li>Bourrage papier</li>\r\n<li>Le papier est coinc&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Le papier est d&eacute;chir&eacute;</li>\r\n<li>Imprimante erreur</li>\r\n<li>Erreur papier</li>\r\n<li>Papier coinc&eacute;</li>\r\n</ul>
202	✅ Nettoyer une imprimante QW410	nettoyer-une-imprimante-qw410-319	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	319	2026-01-19 17:02:58	2026-05-27 18:57:43.214	2026-01-19 17:02:58	\N	\N	<p>Mon imprimante laisse des traces sur les photos.</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel a consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/2ffa177e-793d-40a3-83c5-6bf3a914fc58.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="295" /></p>		f		<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1776762914019" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1776762914019" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Vid&eacute;os &agrave; consulter&nbsp;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1776762914019" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><video style="background-color: #f1f1f1;" controls="controls" width="300" height="150">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/c861715a-2d6d-457b-9d42-a73adf987a33.mp4#t=0.4" />\r\n</video></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Passage du papier pour nettoyer l'imprimante :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><video controls="controls" width="300" height="150">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/05f8b3e8-d018-4c29-ab88-753836643f96.mp4#t=0.4" />\r\n</video></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>L'imprimante laisse des traces</li>\r\n<li>Quelque chose est coinc&eacute; dans l'imprimante</li>\r\n<li>Imprimante &agrave; nettoyer</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment faire pour nettoyer l'imprimante ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi l'imprimante laisse des traces sur les photos ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
228	✅ Personnaliser un cadre photo	personnaliser-un-cadre-photo-345	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	345	2026-05-12 13:55:42	2026-05-27 18:57:45.41	2026-05-12 13:55:42	\N	\N	<p>Je souhaite personnaliser mon cadre photo.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>A consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>Il faut vous rendre sur votre espace manager pour personnalise votre cadre photo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://booth.selfizee.fr/fr/users/login">https://booth.selfizee.fr/fr/users/login</a></p>		f		<div id="heading-1778070140557" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1778070140557" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Personnalisation d'un cadre photo</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1778070140557" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Lorsque vous &ecirc;tes sur votre &eacute;v&eacute;nement, cliquez sur "configurer".</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/a9a4874a-5aec-4d55-81fa-3b1222c104b4.png" alt="" width="661" height="183" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Dans "Animation", cochez "ANIMATION PHOTO".</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp; Vous pouvez &eacute;galement cocher les diff&eacute;rents animations en dessous.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/cd9a9594-c3d8-467b-8bdb-32ba191810a5.png" alt="" width="661" height="373" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "Personnaliser".</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/3d4c6cf0-5d1e-44a9-81d7-8f284a88fe63.png" alt="" width="665" height="382" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "Selfizee" pour d&eacute;couvrir notre catalogue.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/4feaac46-1414-4fa6-829b-8f7be1d3b3a2.png" alt="" width="667" height="102" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">-Choisissez votre th&egrave;me.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/16bcc0f8-3ee3-4fdb-bce4-28e914a0ce59.png" alt="" width="669" height="348" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Personnalisez de A &agrave; Z votre cadre gr&acirc;ces aux outils disponible sur notre logiciel.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/a604edf7-7133-4621-9510-16417289cdc8.png" alt="" width="669" height="369" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Enregistrez en haut &agrave; droite.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/52b37b7b-56bc-4092-8507-22b0abeb1dd9.png" alt="" width="668" height="368" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Votre cadre appara&icirc;t maintenant dans animation.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Aper&ccedil;u vid&eacute;o :&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="530" height="265">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/fbb9f609-5b92-4676-abe2-533876272d00.mp4#t=0.4" /></video></p>\r\n</div>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>je ne sais pas o&ugrave; personnaliser mon cadre photo</li>\r\n<li>je souhaites choisir un mod&egrave;le du catalogue Selfizee</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment personnaliser un cadre photo ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>O&ugrave; trouver des mod&egrave;les du catalogue ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Comment enregistrer mon cadre photo ?</li>\r\n<li>Comment activer les diff&eacute;rentes animations ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
205	Autoriser une application bloquée dans sécurité Windows 10 et 11	autoriser-une-application-bloquee-dans-securite-windows-10-et-11-322	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	322	2026-03-02 14:06:29	2026-05-27 18:57:44.077	2026-03-02 14:06:29	\N	\N	<p>Mon application est bloqu&eacute;e &agrave; cause de Windows 10 ou 11.&nbsp;</p>				f		<p>1- Allez sur le bureau de votre ordinateur sur la borne photo et suivez les &eacute;tapes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/50b92d30-b77b-4339-885b-a47e6a767262.png" alt="" width="576" height="338" /></p>\r\n<p>3- La page "S&eacute;curit&eacute; Windows" va s'ouvrir</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/b393f6e8-4ddf-47ad-81a2-a7b554f2fb5a.png" alt="" width="656" height="258" /></p>\r\n<p>4-</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/3e34b85c-0100-46d6-aca2-e9126ee691e9.png" alt="" width="676" height="301" /></p>\r\n<p>5-</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/b41b17c6-c405-47db-8cd8-7e2e8e5db5df.png" alt="" width="630" height="305" /></p>\r\n<p>6-</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/3ca99722-5419-4e4e-9169-973b3735ed5f.png" alt="" width="758" height="409" /></p>\r\n<p>7-&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/169ee685-fb81-4a32-b892-68b88bf03a45.png" alt="" width="639" height="352" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>8-</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/c2dd8377-2de9-411b-8519-20b7deeaa0c0.png" alt="" width="716" height="426" /></p>	\N				
206	⌛Quel est le format de l'écran d'accueil ? 	quel-est-le-format-de-l-ecran-d-accueil-323	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		DRAFT	323	2026-04-16 13:44:35	2026-05-27 18:57:44.187	\N	\N	\N	<p>Je souhaite personnaliser l'&eacute;cran d'accueil de ma borne photo mais je ne trouves pas le format.&nbsp;</p>		<p>Pour r&eacute;aliser l'&eacute;cran d'accueil il suffit d'aller sur canva ou encore photoshop.&nbsp;<br /><br />Le format est : 1200 x 800 pixels&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Une fois l'&eacute;cran r&eacute;alis&eacute;, rendez-vous sur le manager dans "&Eacute;crans".</p>\r\n<p>Cliquez sur "Voir / &eacute;diter les &eacute;crans".&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/d669476c-63e9-40e2-b535-263aa3f9789a.png" alt="" width="406" height="285" /></p>\r\n<p>Cliquez sur le petit crayon en haut &agrave; droite de l'&eacute;cran noir.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/063efd8f-3efd-4ffc-880d-e546f8e360ef.png" alt="" width="404" height="342" /></p>\r\n<p>Cliquez sur "SUPPRIMER" et glisser votre nouveau fond.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/9ee412fa-9801-4b3d-8b54-61bc912fefbd.png" alt="" width="405" height="304" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>BOUTON</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>		f			\N				
208	✅ Supprimer des événements de la borne photo	supprimer-des-evenements-de-la-borne-photo-325	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	325	2026-04-21 09:08:22	2026-05-27 18:57:44.266	2026-04-21 09:08:22	\N	\N	<p>Ma borne est lente et j'aimerai vider mes &eacute;v&eacute;nements.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel &agrave; consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>La suppression d'&eacute;v&eacute;nements se fait de la m&ecirc;me fa&ccedil;on sur les deux bornes.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/posts/7db2b058-73f5-49a0-870b-c8751a933b03.png" alt="" width="259" height="331" />&nbsp;<img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/17e12512-ee16-464e-89cc-aa11a3f60420.png" alt="" width="378" height="345" /></p>		f		<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1776759163332" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1776759163332" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 1 - Liste des configurations&nbsp;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1776759163332" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Restez appuyer quelques secondes en haut &agrave; gauche de l'&eacute;cran pour entrer dans l'espace administrateur.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Rentrez le mot de passe qui est sur la photo ci-dessous.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/0d0396a0-ebb4-4b31-8fe7-134a9e55e92d.png" alt="" width="389" height="219" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Vous &ecirc;tes maintenant dans la liste des configurations.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/a8ecfe46-93df-46c4-936d-b75816a45162.png" alt="" width="389" height="263" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1776759165870" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1776759165870" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">&Eacute;tape 2 - Suppression des &eacute;v&eacute;nements&nbsp;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1776759165870" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "MES &Eacute;V&Eacute;NEMENTS". Vous allez retrouver tous les anciens &eacute;v&eacute;nements t&eacute;l&eacute;charg&eacute;s.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/80d883dc-cc39-4208-9f40-2b8adecac9a0.png" alt="" width="382" height="258" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur les troits traits &agrave; gauche de la ligne de l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/3cdadffd-67dd-494c-849b-edff7a55ad4d.png" alt="" width="384" height="120" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "Archiver".&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/15e97987-868a-4c3e-9a84-ac0e0d1f32e8.png" alt="" width="385" height="120" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Allez maintenant dans "ARCHIVES".</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/0031da9c-604a-4a6a-9010-4dab996507f5.png" alt="" width="386" height="261" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur les troits petits trait &agrave; gauche de la ligne de l'&eacute;v&eacute;nement et cliquez sur supprimer.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/de8c0863-150e-4f6f-a99f-cb2413cb421f.png" alt="" width="388" height="92" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>borne lente</li>\r\n<li>trop d'&eacute;v&eacute;nements</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment supprimer des &eacute;v&eacute;nements de la borne photo ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi ma borne est plus lente qu'avant ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
209	✅ Gabarit pour l'écran d'accueil 	gabarit-pour-l-ecran-d-accueil-326	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	326	2026-04-21 09:45:32	2026-05-27 18:57:44.316	2026-04-21 09:45:32	\N	\N	<p>Je souhaite personnaliser l'&eacute;cran d'accueil sur la borne photo.&nbsp;</p>		<h2>A consulter :</h2>\r\n<p>Il faut vous rendre sur votre espace manager pour modifier l'&eacute;cran d'accueil.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://booth.selfizee.fr/fr/users/login">https://booth.selfizee.fr/fr/users/login</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>		f		<p>Le format pour personnaliser l'&eacute;cran d'accueil est : <strong>1200x800 pixels&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1776763554732" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1776763554732" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Mise en place de l'&eacute;cran d'accueil</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1776763554732" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Une fois sur votre &eacute;v&eacute;nement, dans l'onglet "Configuration" cliquez sur "Configurer".&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/85a10d97-c131-4be0-a480-6abee94178f6.png" alt="" width="510" height="114" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Allez dans l'onglet "&Eacute;crans".&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/cf516fa4-53d4-47ba-b4b2-d7dc9aa90415.png" alt="" width="505" height="283" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur le stylot en haut &agrave; droite de l'&eacute;cran noir.</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/a446656b-6dd9-4857-b4b5-afa6c39c7c4a.png" alt="" width="506" height="289" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "Voir/&eacute;diter les &eacute;crans".&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/f95b60f6-3246-4637-a0ba-2eb2175e9c90.png" alt="" width="503" height="284" /></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">- Cliquez sur "SUPPRIMER" et glissez votre nouvel &eacute;cran d'accueil.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><img src="/uploads/posts/8df61697-8992-4b54-85eb-cae42402f2b0.png" alt="" width="505" height="252" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br /></p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Je n'arrive pas &agrave; changer mon &eacute;cran d'accueil&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Mon &eacute;cran d'accueil est deform&eacute;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Mon &eacute;cran n'est pas &agrave; la bonne taille&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Quel est le gabarit pour l'acran d'accueil ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Quel est le format pour l'&eacute;cran d'accueil ?</li>\r\n<li>O&ugrave; modifier mon &eacute;cran ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
210	✅ Gabarits magnets 	gabarits-magnets-327	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	327	2026-04-21 09:58:23	2026-05-27 18:57:44.349	2026-04-21 09:58:23	\N	\N	<p>Je ne connais pas les gabarits pour personnaliser les magnets.&nbsp;</p>		<p>Nos gabarits s'ouvrent sur Illustrator, il faut donc la suite adobe sur votre ordinateur.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Si besoin nous pouvons r&eacute;aliser ces magnets pour vous si vous nous envoyez tous les &eacute;l&eacute;ments n&eacute;cessaires.&nbsp;</p>		f		<div class="panel panel-default bootstrap-accordion">\r\n<div id="heading-1776765065300" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1776765065300" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">GABARITS</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1776765065300" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>FACE</strong></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><strong>DOS</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>Je voudrais habiller la borne photo</li>\r\n<li>J'aimerai personnaliser la borne photo</li>\r\n<li>Je n'ai pas les gabarits pour personnaliser la borne photo</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Quels sont les gabarits pour personnaliser la face de la borne photo</li>\r\n<li>Quels sont les gabarits pour personnaliser le dos&nbsp;de la borne photo</li>\r\n</ul>
211	✅ Nettoyer une imprimante DS620	nettoyer-une-imprimante-ds620-328	\N	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph"}]}		PUBLISHED	328	2026-05-06 08:59:21	2026-05-27 18:57:44.434	2026-05-06 08:59:21	\N	\N	<p>Mon imprimante laisse des traces sur les photos.</p>		<h2>Mat&eacute;riel a consulter :</h2>\r\n<p><img src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/e8b81711-0b6f-4ca3-a3d5-779ba8ff6412.png" alt="" width="282" height="330" /></p>		f		<div id="heading-1776762914019" class="panel-heading" role="tab">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title" style="width: 767.6875px;"><a class="bootstrap-accordion-title" role="button" href="#collapse-1776762914019" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Vid&eacute;o &agrave; consulter&nbsp;</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapse-1776762914019" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><video controls="controls" width="300" height="150">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/4b9f3d3a-cffd-4869-9a4d-3a52a6e92507.mp4#t=0.4" />\r\n</video></div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">Passage du papier pour nettoyer l'imprimante :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="panel-body bootstrap-accordion-content"><video controls="controls" width="300" height="150">\r\n<source src="https://crm.konitys.fr//uploads/posts/c01add6c-c733-4d4d-8166-b23bdb6c4834.MOV#t=0.4" />\r\n</video></div>\r\n</div>	\N		<ul>\r\n<li>L'imprimante laisse des traces</li>\r\n<li>Quelque chose est coinc&eacute; dans l'imprimante</li>\r\n<li>Imprimante &agrave; nettoyer</li>\r\n</ul>		<ul>\r\n<li>Comment faire pour nettoyer l'imprimante ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Pourquoi l'imprimante laisse des traces sur les photos ?&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>
